metadata.name: 10/29/2022 Punk 2530 Frontrun and Capitulation
metadata.description: On October 29th, 2022, PunksOTC frontrun robertclarke.eth for Punk 2530. Robert had initially bid 66 ETH, and PunksOTC made a slightly higher bid (66.00000000000000002 ETH) right when the owner accepted the initial 66 ETH bid. A few minutes later, Robert followed up with a 66.25 bid, and PunksOTC capitulated on this bid, selling Punk 2530 to Robert for a quick 0.25 ETH profit.
